* Re-tooled to be more like the prawnto plugin [Chris Scharf]
  - now uses .pdf.writer for template name
  - rails_pdf controller method allows for setting various pdf options
  - helpers can now be used in the templates directly
    (i.e. link_to(...) instead of @view.link_to(...))
* Fixed case where matching view helper might not be available. [Matthew Bass]
* Now compatible with Rails 2.1.0 [Matthew Bass]
* Forked project on GitHub [Matthew Bass]